{"tid":1633000,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] Solomon Yue無割過裝修呀","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:12:08.000Z","uid":82895,"like":307,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed2dd22142a2b6808128bdd797498b615c75624","tid":1633000,"uid":82895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:44:47.000Z","msg":"我唔知某D連登仔英文係咪真係咁差 智障 定係鬼黎 我估係鬼多 竟然話因為SY割 所以要停勇武<br />\n<br />\nSY講緊既係 百萬人既示威有升級係在所難免 但佢依舊支持我地爭取自由呀<br />\n<br />\n繼續做翻黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 黃懲罰啦<br />\n好心咪比D鬼帶風向啦 大個仔啦用下腦<br />\n屌撚曬三毛同狗臥底老母呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sODnoG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsODnoG7.jpg&h=7d9d3c3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48ad7a857f75edad862df897dabd8fdda049ee48","tid":1633000,"uid":258696,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"17a19cde6187a68fb421220549a027debfacdaf8","tid":1633000,"uid":81424,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:46:02.000Z","msg":"黑紅裝修<br />\n藍罷買<br />\n黃幫襯"},{"pid":"f66b1c5656f8004a761257a9d104f783e58c6868","tid":1633000,"uid":82895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40b0a42b9d7f3499a39170f4737c21a0936b7688","tid":1633000,"uid":57438,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"道德高地呀"},{"pid":"41f893b5829651a2ef1491c869a6f625949a05f2","tid":1633000,"uid":82895,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"咪撚比鬼利用sy言論 分化啦 <br />\n麻煩自己睇清楚sy講咩"},{"pid":"3d5b246e4c64c619107e05f34dfb9932f7c4efe1","tid":1633000,"uid":82895,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"40b0a42b9d7f3499a39170f4737c21a0936b7688","tid":1633000,"uid":57438,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"道德高地呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"講得岩 所以做野要有原則 藍唔好裝修 主力搞黑 同政府"},{"pid":"bb413c5ba093187f94eff310ab1df28e91448c49","tid":1633000,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:48:07.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7a1b8b6758e9b1717038adafd0d7b251f14fd2","tid":1633000,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"今日風向：勇武退場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631974</a><br />\n-